Kastor
------
Log-structured object storage.


*Requirements

  Following programs are requred to build
	- gcc >= 4.1 with C++ support
    - Tokyo Cabinet >= 1.4.9
	- ruby >= 1.8  (ruby is used as a preprocessor)


*Installation

  Simply run ./configure && make && make install

    $ ./configure
    $ make
    $ sudo make install


*Usage

    kastor <storage> [port=3000]

  Example:

    $ kastor store 5000


